PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,FThe number of cases of breast cancer
OL,7,Fin women under 50 has risen by 5% in
OL,8,Fone year, according to new analysis.
OL,10,FIt comes as the charity CoppaFeel!
OL,11,Fclaimed younger people with symptoms
OL,12,Fof the disease are "routinely
OL,13,Fdismissed" by health professionals.
OL,15,FIt is now calling for a seven-minute
OL,16,Frisk assessment, which looks at
OL,17,Ffactors such as family history, to be
OL,18,Fadopted, in a bid to spot those who
OL,19,Fneed earlier or more frequent breast
OL,20,Fscreening.
OL,26,@tD@TOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
