FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,FThe NHS invites women for a mammogram
OL,7,F` an x-ray of the breast ` from the
OL,8,Fage of 50 until their 71st birthday.
OL,10,FHowever, analysis by CoppaFeel!, which
OL,11,Fwas founded by twin sisters Kris and
OL,12,FMaren Hallenga after Kris was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer at 23,
OL,14,Fsuggests rates of the disease are
OL,15,Frising in younger people.
OL,17,FAccording to its new report, one in
OL,18,Fsix people diagnosed with breast
OL,19,Fcancer are aged 49 and under.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,FDiagnoses in people under 30 jumped by
OL,7,F78% from 2001 to 2019 and from 2022 to
OL,8,F2023, breast cancer rates increased by
OL,9,F5% among 25 to 49 year olds.
OL,11,FThe charity said patients diagnosed
OL,12,Fwith breast cancer under 50 are almost
OL,13,Ftwice as likely to have late-stage
OL,14,Fcancer compared with someone in their
OL,15,F60s, while under 25s are more than
OL,16,Ftwice as likely to be diagnosed with
OL,17,Flate-stage disease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,FSophie Dopierala-Bull, director of
OL,7,Fservices and engagement, CoppaFeel!,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Early diagnosis depends too
OL,9,Fheavily on whether young people know
OL,10,Ftheir bodies, whether they feel
OL,11,Fconfident seeking help, whether they
OL,12,Fcan access healthcare, and whether
OL,13,Fthey are taken seriously when they get
OL,14,Fthere.
OL,16,F"Awareness matters ` CoppaFeel! has
OL,17,Fspent more than 15 years helping young
OL,18,Fpeople know their bodies and feel
OL,19,Fconfident seeking help.
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,F"But awareness alone cannot carry the
OL,7,Fweight of a system that was not built
OL,8,Fwith young people in mind."
OL,10,FCoppaFeel! is calling for a pilot of a
OL,11,Fseven-minute risk assessment which
OL,12,Flooks at family history, genetic
OL,13,Ffactors and breast density to help
OL,14,Ffind patients who may benefit from
OL,15,Fearlier screening rather than relying
OL,16,Fon age alone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,FIt has also recommended that breast
OL,7,Fawareness should be built into routine
OL,8,FNHS appointments and said clinical
OL,9,Fbreast cancer trials should include at
OL,10,Fleast one in six patients under 50.
OL,12,FMs Dopierala-Bull added: "We need
OL,13,Fscreening based on risk, research that
OL,14,Fincludes younger people, and a
OL,15,Fhealthcare system that treats young
OL,16,Fpeople's breast cancer as the urgent
OL,17,Fissue it is."
OL,26,@tD@ZOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
