PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,FErin Kennedy, Paralympic gold
OL,7,Fmedallist and CoppaFeel! ambassador,
OL,8,Fsaid she was at the peak of her
OL,9,Fsporting career when she was diagnosed
OL,10,Fwith triple negative breast cancer at
OL,11,F29.
OL,13,F"Breast cancer was not something I
OL,14,Fthought would become part of my
OL,15,Fstory," she said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,F"I was lucky that I knew my body and
OL,7,Facted when something felt wrong. But
OL,8,Fno young person's outcome should
OL,9,Fdepend on luck, or on whether someone
OL,10,Fbelieves they are old enough to have
OL,11,Fbreast cancer."
OL,13,FDr Elizabeth Lynch, a GP and member of
OL,14,FCoppaFeel!'s medical advisory group,
OL,15,Fsaid a conversation lasting minutes
OL,16,Fcould help younger people understand
OL,17,Fwhat is normal and when to seek help.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
