FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,FShe said: "Although the prevalence of
OL,7,Fbreast cancer in younger people is
OL,8,Flow, there are identifiable risk
OL,9,Ffactors that may highlight those that
OL,10,Fneed additional support, and a brief
OL,11,Fchat would ensure this cohort was
OL,12,Fidentified by their healthcare
OL,13,Fprofessional, their worries and
OL,14,Fconcerns addressed, and tailored,
OL,15,Fappropriate and timely intervention
OL,16,Foffered."
OL,26,@nD@KOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
