FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "It is unacceptable
OL,8,Fthat people have faced delays in
OL,9,Freceiving cancer diagnosis and care,
OL,10,Fand our thoughts are with all those
OL,11,Fwho have been let down.
OL,13,F"We are determined to help people of
OL,14,Fall ages and backgrounds get faster
OL,15,Fdiagnoses, quicker treatment, and the
OL,16,Fsupport they need to live well for
OL,17,Flonger.
OL,26,@oD@TOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782398899
OL,3,CCall for risk-based breast cancer
OL,4,Cscreening as cases in under 50s rise
OL,6,F"Through our National Cancer Plan, all
OL,7,Fpatients will receive a personalised
OL,8,Fplan from 2026, covering treatment,
OL,9,Fmental health, employment, and
OL,10,Ffinancial support.
OL,12,F"We are also removing age-based
OL,13,Fbarriers to clinical trials, ensuring
OL,14,Fyoung adults can access the most
OL,15,Finnovative treatments available."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@aO]
